Usage: rename_pg_library [-help] -cell_list_map_file <string>
                         -merge_library_list_file <string> -output <string>
                         -output_library <string>

-help                                 # Prints out the command usage
-cell_list_map_file <string>          # oldCellname newCellName
                                      # (string, required)
-merge_library_list_file <string>     # <absolute library path>
                                      # (string, required)
-output <string>                      # <directory name> (string, required)
-output_library <string>              # newLibraryName (string, required)